**Properties** are used to build custom forms and gather input from the user.

## Types of Properties

* [User-Defined Properties](/tutorials/properties/user-defined): Properties you can create on demand.

platformOS also provides a few Properties for you to use:

* [Custom Addresses](/tutorials/properties/custom-addresses): used to add one or many addresses to the configuration.

* [Custom Images](/tutorials/properties/custom-images): used to add one or many images to the configuration.

* [Custom Attachments](/tutorials/properties/custom-attachments): used to add one or many files to the configuration.
